[{"id":"VR871076","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<p class=\"stem_paragraph\">A beam of electrons, all traveling at the same speed, is directed at a double slit with a distance <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"lowercase d\"><math alttext=\"lowercase d\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>d</mi></math></span></span> between the two openings. A screen is placed a distance <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"uppercase D is much greater than lowercase d\"><math alttext=\"uppercase D is much greater than lowercase d\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>D</mi><mo>≫</mo><mi>d</mi></math></span></span> beyond the slits and is illuminated when struck by an electron. After some time, a pattern develops on the screen consisting of a bright fringe directly in front of the slits, and alternating dark and bright fringes on both sides of the central bright fringe. Counting from the central bright fringe toward the right, the distance between the second and the sixth bright fringes is measured to be <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"delta x\"><math alttext=\"delta x\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Δ</mi><mi>x</mi></math></span></span>. What is the approximate momentum of the electrons?</p>\n","rubricRef":"VR871076_rubric","choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"the fraction with numerator uppercase D h, and denominator lowercase d delta x\"><math alttext=\"the fraction with numerator uppercase D h, and denominator lowercase d delta x\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mfrac><mrow><mi>D</mi><mi>h</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Δ</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"3 times the fraction with numerator uppercase D h, and denominator lowercase d delta x\"><math alttext=\"3 times the fraction with numerator uppercase D h, and denominator lowercase d delta x\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>3</mn><mfrac><mrow><mi>D</mi><mi>h</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Δ</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"4 times the fraction with numerator uppercase D h, and denominator lowercase d delta x\"><math alttext=\"4 times the fraction with numerator uppercase D h, and denominator lowercase d delta x\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>4</mn><mfrac><mrow><mi>D</mi><mi>h</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Δ</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"6 times the fraction with numerator uppercase D h, and denominator lowercase d delta x\"><math alttext=\"6 times the fraction with numerator uppercase D h, and denominator lowercase d delta x\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>6</mn><mfrac><mrow><mi>D</mi><mi>h</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Δ</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac></math></span></span></p>"],"answer":2}]